Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错综复杂的王宫形势
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.06,0:23:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对孤身奋战的皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.79,0:23:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女向她伸出了援助之手
